<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">قَالَ أَبُو بَكْرٍ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">"الْإِيمَانُ عِنْدَنَا قَوْلٌ وَعَمَلٌ، وَيَزِيدُ وَيَنْقُصُ"</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>آخر الكتاب،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>والحمد لله رب العالمين،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وصلى الله على محمد وآله وسلم.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>